12         = {{flat list|\n*Jackson\n*Riley\n}}\n| length12        = 4:25\n\n| title13         = [[Cry (Michael Jackson song)|Cry]]\n| writer13        = [[R. Kelly|Robert Kelly]]\n| extra13         = {{flat list|\n*Jackson\n*Kelly\n}}\n| length13        = 5:01\n\n| title14         = The Lost Children\n| writer14        = Jackson\n| extra14         = Jackson\n| length14        = 4:00\n\n| title15         = Whatever Happens\n| note15          = featuring [[Carlos Santana]]\n| writer15        = {{flat list|\n*Jackson\n*Riley\n}}\n| extra15         = {{flat list|\n*Jackson\n*Riley\n}}\n| length15        = 4:56\n\n| title16         = Threatened\n| writer16        = {{flat list|\n*Jackson\n*Jerkins\n*Jerkins III\n*Daniels\n}}\n| extra16         = {{flat list|\n*Jackson\n*Jerkins\n}}\n| length16        = 4:19\n}}\n\n'''Notes'''\n*\"Unbreakable\" features a rap verse by [[The Notorious B.I.G.]] The rap verse was originally from the song \"[[You Can't Stop the Reign (song)|You Can't Stop the Reign]]\" by [[Shaquille O'Neal]]. It was written by Carl McIntosh, Jane Eugene and Steve Nichol.\n*\"Break of Dawn\", \"2000 Watts\" and \"Threatened\" were excluded from the original Chinese release.<ref>{{cite web|title=\u8fc8\u514b\u5c14\u00b7\u6770\u514b\u900aMichael Jackson:\u5929\u4e0b\u65e0\u654cInvincible-\u97f3\u4e50-\u5353\u8d8a\u4e9a\u9a6c\u900a |url=https://www.amazon.cn/dp/B002FL3KCM|publisher=Amazon.cn|accessdate=2011-01-04}}</ref> In the Chinese edition of the [[box set]] ''[[The Collection (Michael Jackson album)|The Collection]]'' released in 2013, all 16 tracks are included.<ref>{{cite web|title=\u8fc8\u514b\u5c14\u2022\u6770\u514b\u900a:\u661f\u5149\u4f20\u5947(5CD) [\u5957\u88c5]|url=https://www.amazon.cn/gp/product/B00C9T6VNK|publisher=Amazon.cn|accessdate=2013-04-23}}</ref>\n\n==Personnel==\nCredits adapted from ''Invincible'' album liner notes.<ref name=\"linernotes\"/>\n\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[Michael Jackson]] \u2013 lead vocals {{small|(all tracks)}}, 